@Bioluminescence, You are awesome for responding!

I'm not intending to sound sarcastic here, but it would really be nice to have someone with definitive knowledge of League of Legends lore answer this question. As you yourself have pointed out you are "not a narrative team Rioter".

@Riot, could we actually have a narrative team rioter respond to this thread so that we could have a definitive answer?
